checkpoints on every corner.

01:18:02.812 --> 01:18:03.978
Lie low.

01:18:03.980 --> 01:18:05.446
For how long?

01:18:05.448 --> 01:18:07.314
As long as it takes.

01:18:07.316 --> 01:18:09.116
