shit out of me, it worked.

01:18:38.414 --> 01:18:40.534
Hey, Mona told me
about the dance.

01:18:41.149 --> 01:18:42.349
I'm really glad you did it.

01:18:42.351 --> 01:18:44.251
Thanks.

01:18:44.253 --> 01:18:46.253
And it's good
you're acting again, too.

01:18:50.459 --> 01:18:51.992
